article.headline: Robinson guides Little Rock to 80-66 victory over Murray State

images.name: Murray State Racers vs. Little Rock : Full Highlights
images.caption: Murray State Racers vs. Little Rock : Full Highlights

article.linkText: Robinson guides Little Rock to 80-66 victory over Murray State
article.story: LITTLE ROCK, Ark. -- — Khalen Robinson scored 16 points as Little Rock beat Murray State 80-66 on Monday night. Robinson also contributed 14 rebounds for the Trojans (6-6). Deantoni Gordon scored 15 points and added seven rebounds. Bradley Douglas was 5 of 10 shooting (4 for 7 from 3-point range) to finish with 14 points. Nick Ellington finished with 17 points and five blocks for the Racers (3-8). Rob Perry added 12 points for Murray State. In addition, Brian Moore Jr. had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
